# speqtro.vendors — Vendored external academic tools
#
# This package contains inference-only code from external research tools,
# adapted for direct import within speqtro. Each subpackage corresponds
# to one external tool:
#
#   cascade  — CASCADE 2.0, 13C NMR shift prediction (TensorFlow)
#   chefnmr  — ChefNMR, NMR-to-structure elucidation (PyTorch)
#   dp5      — DP5/DP4, Bayesian NMR structure verification (scipy)
#   ssin     — SSIN, IR functional group detection (PyTorch)
#   mspred   — ms-pred/ICEBERG, MS/MS fragmentation prediction (PyTorch+DGL)
#
# See CITATIONS.md and THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES for attribution and licenses.
